Buisnesses need computers to do things effectively and decrease the cost of imputations.
We analyze data that companies gather in csv files and spreadsheets, organize them in databases, later than use that data to train models for Machine Learning, Deep Learning.
Instead of humans analyzing data, we make machines analyze data for efficient and improved comptutations in data.
Businesses love the concept of Machine learning as it increases the profitability of companies with outputs and predictions coming out from Machine Learning models.
Data scientists are people that make data use-less to use-full.